00:16:23,320 --> 00:16:24,359
Yes.

278
00:16:24,479 --> 00:16:25,039
My son bought me a house

279
00:16:25,119 --> 00:16:27,119
in the city.

280
00:16:27,280 --> 00:16:28,400
