every time he comes back,

285
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:44,040
and he doesn't even have time
to talk to me.

286
00:16:45,760 --> 00:16:48,119
Since you two came
all the way from city,

287
00:16:48,479 --> 00:16:50,199
