for me.

296
00:17:33,599 --> 00:17:35,160
If you are trying to
save this relationship

297
00:17:35,599 --> 00:17:37,760
by treating me well.

298
00:17:38,359 --> 00:17:40,199
Then you should give up.

299
00:17:42,760 --> 00:17:43,640
Fanlv.

300
00:17:44,839 --> 00:17:45,880
You're wrong.

301
00:17:47,239 --> 00:17:47,959
I've never thought about

302
00:17:48,079 --> 00:17:49,479
saving our relationship.

303
00:17:51,119 --> 00:17:52,199
I know that

304
00:17:53,319 --> 00:17:56,959
