305
00:17:59,439 --> 00:18:01,199
and you will never forgive me.

306
00:18:01,719 --> 00:18:04,920
I saved you because I must.

307
00:18:06,119 --> 00:18:07,439
Life is so valuable.

308
00:18:08,560 --> 00:18:10,000
I can't watch anyone

309
00:18:10,079 --> 00:18:11,239
giving it up so easy.

310
00:18:13,079 --> 00:18:15,119
Not to mention you are my family.

311
00:18:15,880 --> 00:18:17,760
If something happens to me today,

312
00:18:20,160 --> 00:18:23,199
you will save me too, right?

313
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:28,400
I've walked here so many times.

314
00:18:30,280 --> 00:18:31,239
But it feels different

315
00:18:31,319 --> 00:18:32,680
every time I'm here.

316
00:18:35,199 --> 00:18:36,400
I still remember the first time

317
00:18:38,199 --> 00:18:39,560
when I went to your home

318
00:18:40,479 --> 00:18:41,959
to report to your dad.

319
00:18:43,520 --> 00:18:45,119
It was early spring at that time,

320
00:18:45,479 --> 00:18:47,199
and the whole city
was vibrant,

321
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:49,880
just like my hometown.

322
00:18:50,839 --> 00:18:52,400
I just graduated at that time,

323
00:18:53,479 --> 00:18:55,520
and I stood out from many competitors

324
00:18:56,719 --> 00:18:58,839
to be your dad's assistant.

325
00:18:59,920 --> 00:19:01,319
To be honest,

326
00:19:02,079 --> 00:19:03,400
dad is really good to me.

327
00:19:04,239 --> 00:19:05,719
He promoted me as best as he could.

328
00:19:07,199 --> 00:19:08,640
I feel like that

329
00:19:09,520 --> 00:19:10,920
I'm like the bud on the tree,

330
00:19:12,199 --> 00:19:14,079
and my life has just started.

331
00:19:15,520 --> 00:19:17,119
Everything looked hopeful.

332
00:19:17,959 --> 00:19:21,040
Last fall I was also here.

333
00:19:21,319 --> 00:19:22,599
That day you had the abortion.

334
00:19:24,199 --> 00:19:25,959
I was walking here by myself,

335
00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:27,880
and the wind was so strong,

336
00:19:29,079 --> 00:19:30,760
making me feel sad.

337
00:19:33,599 --> 00:19:36,119
I feel regretful for not cherishing you.

338
00:19:37,359 --> 00:19:38,839
I don't know why

339
00:19:39,119 --> 00:19:40,359
life is still so harsh on me

340
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:43,560
when I'm trying this hard.

341
00:19:46,359 --> 00:19:48,040
Today we are on this road again.

342
00:19:48,880 --> 00:19:50,880
I hope there's no end on this road.

343
00:19:51,719 --> 00:19:52,719
Then,

344
00:19:54,119 --> 00:19:55,959
I will be able to walk with you forever.

345
00:19:57,959 --> 00:19:59,680
If we reach the end of the road,

346
00:20:02,760 --> 00:20:06,280
so does our marriage.

347
00:20:23,719 --> 00:20:25,239
You finally agreed to get divorced.

348
00:20:26,920 --> 00:20:28,280
I've promised Mr Jiang that

349
