once you get better,

350
00:20:32,640 --> 00:20:34,040
we will get divorced.

351
00:20:42,920 --> 00:20:45,359
Fanlv, you should know that

352
00:20:45,800 --> 00:20:47,160
I care about you.

353
00:20:47,760 --> 00:20:49,319
I don't want to get divorced either.

354
00:20:50,479 --> 00:20:52,400
If fate brings you to me,

355
00:20:52,520 --> 00:20:53,839
to hurt you or make you so desperate

356
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:56,839
that you want to destroy yourself,

357
00:20:57,280 --> 00:20:58,959
then I'd rather fight the fate.

358
00:21:00,920 --> 00:21:02,760
I'd rather step out of your life.

359
00:21:09,319 --> 00:21:10,599
Your dad was right.

360
00:21:11,199 --> 00:21:12,439
Our marriage might have been

361
00:21:12,520 --> 00:21:13,680
a mistake from the very beginning.

362
00:21:16,079 --> 00:21:17,920
It's like ocean versus fire.

363
00:21:18,800 --> 00:21:20,439
One person has to disappear,

364
00:21:21,400 --> 00:21:23,079
then everything can come to an end.

365
00:21:23,959 --> 00:21:25,760
The best way that a person can get cured

366
00:21:25,920 --> 00:21:27,319
is to forget about all the past.

367
00:21:31,040 --> 00:21:35,439
Fanlv, we've been husband and wife.

368
00:21:36,800 --> 00:21:38,000
I just hope that I'm able to

369
00:21:40,359 --> 00:21:42,079
watch you from far away

370
00:21:42,400 --> 00:21:43,680
without bothering you

371
00:21:45,119 --> 00:21:47,239
