00:21:56,040 --> 00:21:57,040
You are right.

374
00:21:57,359 --> 00:21:58,839
He really does.

375
00:22:00,599 --> 00:22:03,239
Qunfei, it's actually him.

376
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:05,719
It's been so quiet most of the time.

377
00:22:05,839 --> 00:22:07,079
But it feels so lively today.

378
00:22:07,199 --> 00:22:08,760
Two more dishes will be ready.

379
00:22:08,839 --> 00:22:09,640
Aunt.

380
00:22:09,760 --> 00:22:11,520
Excuse me, we want to
ask you about someone.

381
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:14,000
Do you know him?

382
00:22:14,239 --> 00:22:16,119
This is the son of Li family
from the village nearby.

383
00:22:16,359 --> 00:22:17,479
Do you know his full name?

384
00:22:17,599 --> 00:22:18,640
No. I don't know.

385
00:22:18,959 --> 00:22:20,199
Is he a friend of your son?

386
00:22:20,319 --> 00:22:20,920
Yes.

387
00:22:21,040 --> 00:22:22,199
They've grown up together
since they are kids.

388
00:22:22,319 --> 00:22:24,439
They were good friends at school.

389
00:22:24,599 --> 00:22:25,239
Qunfei, we gotta go.

390
00:22:25,319 --> 00:22:26,079
Ok.

391
00:22:26,280 --> 00:22:27,880
Aunt, we owe you this meal.

392
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:29,119
We will treat you to meal

