405
00:23:06,719 --> 00:23:08,359
They don't know we are coming.

406
00:23:13,119 --> 00:23:14,079
Mr. Lei.

407
00:23:14,520 --> 00:23:15,920
I really can't understand.

408
00:23:17,640 --> 00:23:18,719
Both Lin Xiangyuan and I

409
00:23:18,800 --> 00:23:20,359
came from the small village.

410
00:23:21,680 --> 00:23:24,199
How come he becomes a person

411
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:27,560
who only cares for money and fame?

412
00:23:28,079 --> 00:23:30,800
Qunfei, as for intrinsic quality,

413
00:23:30,920 --> 00:23:31,439
Lin Xiangyuan might not be

414
00:23:31,560 --> 00:23:32,959
as bad as we thought.

415
00:23:33,560 --> 00:23:34,800
You saw it just now.

416
00:23:36,640 --> 00:23:38,599
I guess that Lin Xiangyuan
used all the money

417
00:23:39,199 --> 00:23:40,800
he made to build the road,

418
00:23:40,880 --> 00:23:42,119
and school for this village.

419
00:23:42,280 --> 00:23:43,479
All the kids in this village

420
00:23:43,599 --> 00:23:44,760
may also know that

421
00:23:44,880 --> 00:23:46,199
as long as they study well,

422
00:23:46,359 --> 00:23:47,719
they can be like Lin Xiangyuan

423
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:49,239
and change their fates.

424
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:51,800
As he has a successful career,
he doesn't forget how he started.

425
00:23:52,439 --> 00:23:53,640
Then why doesn't he bring his mom

426
00:23:53,800 --> 00:23:55,319
to Shanghai?

427
00:23:56,439 --> 00:23:57,560
Think about it.

428
00:23:58,400 --> 00:23:59,599
His mom is his only family member

429
00:23:59,680 --> 00:24:01,160
in this world.

430
00:24:01,800 --> 00:24:03,959
She is also his biggest weakness.

431
00:24:05,040 --> 00:24:06,000
Lin Xiangyuan seems to stay

432
00:24:06,119 --> 00:24:07,800
in the center of hurricane.

433
00:24:08,359 --> 00:24:09,880
If he makes one mistake,

434
00:24:10,199 --> 00:24:11,560
then there might be

435
00:24:11,680 --> 00:24:13,239
a huge price that he needs to pay.

436
00:24:14,160 --> 00:24:17,119
So he wants his mom to be
far away from Shanghai.

437
00:24:19,359 --> 00:24:20,880
I see, Mr. Lei.

438
00:24:21,199 --> 00:24:23,479
Are you acting cold to Du Xiaosu recently

439
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:25,839
because of the same reason?

