a house in the city.

448
00:25:39,800 --> 00:25:42,479
So do you know where he lives now?

449
00:25:42,680 --> 00:25:45,280
I remember it's a place called
Happy Neighborhood in Shanghai.

450
00:25:45,760 --> 00:25:47,239
Happy Neighborhood.

451
00:25:47,800 --> 00:25:48,959
Ok. Thank you very much.

452
00:25:49,119 --> 00:25:50,160
Thank you!

453
00:25:50,680 --> 00:25:51,880
Qunfei, let's go back to Shanghai.

454
00:25:52,040 --> 00:25:53,079
Ok.

455
00:26:25,040 --> 00:26:26,400
You don't have to follow me every day.

456
00:26:27,359 --> 00:26:30,079
I said that I won't commit suicide

457
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:35,239
because there are things that I can't let go.

458
00:26:36,359 --> 00:26:38,160
Dad is getting old and

459
00:26:40,599 --> 00:26:42,119
