460
00:26:50,400 --> 00:26:51,479
Don't be upset.

461
00:26:52,359 --> 00:26:53,680
Your illness will be cured.

462
00:26:54,040 --> 00:26:55,719
I will take care of you as well.

463
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:57,760
Lin Xiangyuan,

464
00:26:59,520 --> 00:27:01,199
I don't need you to feel pity for me.

465
00:27:01,400 --> 00:27:02,520
Are you silly?

466
00:27:03,199 --> 00:27:05,160
I don't feel pity for you.

467
00:27:06,439 --> 00:27:07,599
Trust me.

468
00:27:07,880 --> 00:27:11,000
You will get better for sure
since you have me.

469
00:27:14,319 --> 00:27:15,959
You can be with me for now,

470
00:27:17,000 --> 00:27:18,680
