at that time?

474
00:27:29,560 --> 00:27:32,640
Like I said before, you are
my family member.

475
00:27:33,319 --> 00:27:35,000
Of course I will care about you.

476
00:27:35,719 --> 00:27:37,319
Even though after we get divorced,

477
00:27:37,599 --> 00:27:39,040
as long as you need me,

478
00:27:39,599 --> 00:27:41,239
I will be here any time

479
00:27:43,560 --> 00:27:45,760
