00:30:23,599 --> 00:30:25,680
Would you like to have a second thought?

506
00:30:27,079 --> 00:30:28,239
There's no such need.

507
00:30:28,439 --> 00:30:29,920
We've already decided.

508
00:30:32,199 --> 00:30:33,560
Then tell me about

509
00:30:33,680 --> 00:30:35,119
