522
00:31:00,199 --> 00:31:01,479
No, we must get divorced.

523
00:31:03,760 --> 00:31:04,880
Our characteristics are too different.

524
00:31:05,040 --> 00:31:06,079
She is right.

525
00:31:07,359 --> 00:31:08,719
We don't match in many ways.

526
00:31:08,839 --> 00:31:10,199
Such as?

527
00:31:11,760 --> 00:31:12,920
Do we have to say?

528
00:31:13,119 --> 00:31:14,760
Yes, you have to say it.

529
00:31:17,040 --> 00:31:17,920
Alright.

530
00:31:18,839 --> 00:31:20,160
I can tell the details.

531
00:31:20,400 --> 00:31:21,880
I'm from a small village in Guizhou,

532
00:31:23,199 --> 00:31:24,760
while she grew up in Shanghai,

533
00:31:24,880 --> 00:31:26,000
and she went to study abroad.

534
00:31:26,239 --> 00:31:28,040
She likes the kind of man

535
00:31:28,199 --> 00:31:29,439
who is wise, brave, and humorous.

536
00:31:30,040 --> 00:31:31,040
However, I have to act so carefully

537
00:31:32,239 --> 00:31:35,599
all the time every day.

538
00:31:35,800 --> 00:31:36,880
I admit that

539
00:31:37,079 --> 00:31:39,040
when I first tried to get closer to her,

540
00:31:40,400 --> 00:31:43,920
